About Event

​Build faster inside Unreal Engine 5 using AI-powered analysis.

​This is a hands-on Vibe Coding Night where we’ll use Cline and the Unreal Engine Analyzer (MPC Server) to explore, debug, and iterate on real UE5 projects — live. No slides. No spectators. Just world-building, gameplay logic, and AI-assisted chaos.

​Bring a laptop that can run Unreal Engine 5 (Gaming / dev-grade machines strongly recommended)

​Perfect for:

​Game devs

​Real-time 3D + simulation builders

​Engine ne
